videos.headline: Caitlin Clark drains a 3 from logo range
videos.description: Caitlin Clark scores her first points of the national title game by draining a deep 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One Play (Caitlin Clark drains a 3 from logo range) 2023/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Flau'jae Johnson gets fired up after the and-1
videos.description: Flau'jae Johnson gets tripped up by Caitlin Clark and finishes the and-1 for LSU.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One Play (Flau'jae Johnson gets fired up after the and-1) 2023/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark splashes her fourth 3-pointer of the 1st quarter
videos.description: Caitlin Clark makes it look easy with her fourth 3-pointer of the opening quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark splashes her fourth 3-pointer of the 1st quarter) 2023/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jasmine Carson extends LSU's lead with catch-and-shoot 3
videos.description: Jasmine Carson catches the ball at the top of the key and drains a 3-pointer for LSU.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Jasmine Carson extends LSU's lead with catch-and-shoot 3) 2023/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark drops a beautiful backdoor dime for Iowa
videos.description: Caitlin Clark finds Kate Martin with a silky backdoor pass for the Hawkeyes.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark drops a beautiful backdoor dime for Iowa) 2023/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jasmine Carson electrifies the crowd with transition 3
videos.description: Jasmine Carson makes her fourth 3-pointer in a row as LSU builds a double-digit lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Jasmine Carson electrifies the crowd with transition 3) 2023/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jasmine Carson caps off perfect half with buzzer-beating 3
videos.description: Jasmine Carson completes an incredible first half with a banked-in 3-pointer at the buzzer for LSU.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One Play (Jasmine Carson caps off perfect half with buzzer-beating 3) 2023/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark heads to the bench after third first-half foul
videos.description: Caitlin Clark gets called for the offensive foul and hits the bench for the Hawkeyes.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark heads to the bench after third first-half foul) 2023/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark sets record for most points in a single tournament with trey
videos.description: Caitlin Clark hits a fadeaway 3-pointer to set the NCAA tournament record for most points all time in a single tourney.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark sets record for most points in a single tournament with trey) 2023/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark gets T'd up for fourth personal foul
videos.description: Caitlin Clark gets called for the technical foul, her fourth foul of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark gets T'd up for fourth personal foul) 2023/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kim Mulkey gets emotional after LSU sinks dagger 3-pointer
videos.description: Kim Mulkey lets her emotions show after Kateri Poole sinks a game-sealing 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Kim Mulkey gets emotional after LSU sinks dagger 3-pointer) 2023/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: 'Can't see me!' Angel Reese trolls Caitlin Clark late in the game
videos.description: Angel Reese is hyped over LSU's big lead in the fourth quarter, pointing to her ring finger and flashing the "can't see me" at Caitlin Clark.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play ('Can't see me!' Angel Reese trolls Caitlin Clark late in the 4th) 2023/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kim Mulkey fights back tears after LSU wins national championship
videos.description: Kim Mulkey has tears of joy as she opens up about what LSU's national title means to her.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Kim Mulkey fights back tears after LSU wins national championship) 2023/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: LSU celebrates first NCAA title in program history
videos.description: LSU soaks it in after defeating Iowa 102-85 to take home the women's NCAA national championship.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (LSU celebrates first NCAA title in program history) 2023/04/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Morris details why LSU deserves respect after title win
videos.description: Alexis Morris describes how she became a defensive stopper in the NCAA National Championship victory against Iowa, 102-85, and why LSU deserves respect.

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCW Interview (Morris LSU) 230402

videos.headline: LSU takes down Caitlin Clark and Iowa to win first title in program history
videos.description: LSU sets an NCAA title game record with a 102-point performance in the Tigers' win over Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (LSU takes down Caitlin Clark and Iowa to win first title in program history) 2023/04/02 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Reese: LSU began piecing things together in summer
videos.description: While being asked about the cohesion of nine new players in 2023, Angel Reese pinpoints the moment the national champion Tigers began to mesh.

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCW Interview (Angel interview 2) 230402

videos.headline: LSU wins first title, breaks record for points scored
videos.description: Ignited by Jasmine Carson's perfect first half (21 points), the 3-seed Tigers record the most points in NCAA title history in a 102-85 win over 2-seed Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCW Highlight (LSU Iowa) 230402 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams praises LSU's chemistry and team effort
videos.description: Following the title win over Iowa, LaDazhia Williams says Jasmine Carson was a "big bang" off the bench and credits the Tigers' collective effort.

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCW Interview (Williams LSU) 230402

videos.headline: Angel Reese explains gesture toward Caitlin Clark
videos.description: LSU's Angel Reese explains why she gestured "can't see me" towards Caitlin Clark late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Interview (Angel Reese explains gesture toward Caitlin Clark) 2023/4/2

videos.headline: How bench depth, Morris' late jump made LSU history
videos.description: SEC Now's Steffi Sorensen and Alyssa Lang analyze how Jasmine Carson's threes lit a fire under LSU and Alexis Morris' fourth-quarter performance secured the victory.

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCW Analysis (LSU Bench) 230402 ESHEET

videos.headline: Season Recap: LSU makes history with title win
videos.description: Take a look at the Tigers' improbable journey to a championship title that included the immersion of nine new players on the roster in 2023.

tracking.trackingName: SEC_NCW Feature (LSU season recap) 230402 ESHEET

videos.headline: Iowa coach voices frustrations with refs in title game
videos.description: Iowa head coach Lisa Bluder explains why she didn't agree with the way the national championship game against LSU was officiated.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Presser (Iowa coach voices frustrations with refs in title game) 2023/4/2

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark tears up while talking about her legacy
videos.description: Hawkeyes superstar Caitlin Clark gets emotional when asked about her legacy with Iowa basketball.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Presser (Caitlin Clark tears up while talking about her legacy) 2023/04/02
